# Single source of truth for the sing-box fork image tag.
# Sourced by singbox-run.sh and singbox-watchdog.sh (PRODUCT-MATURITY-LOOP D10).
# Bump this ONE line after a fork rebuild so the watchdog never resurrects a
# stale image during an outage. Keep in sync with the tag in CLAUDE.md / docs.
SINGBOX_IMAGE="sing-box-fork:v1.13.6-userapi"
